#i5 At any given time, VeraGames has millions of servers crunching data to provide the best experience for each Player. The way that they handle something like call/cc is to temporarily speed up one player's mind by allocating it more servers. 

#i5 One of VeraGames' crucial early discoveries was that the human mind believes it has a fixed speed at which it processes information. The mind does not perceptibly speed up. Instead, the world slows down. These pseudo-relativistic effects are used to great effect in the Realm. ((lol effect!)) 

